{"tid":1939101,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"寫給妳6年回憶的一封信","createTime":"2020-03-23T03:07:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-23T12:30:00.000Z","uid":192745,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"784020b066f47ae689355563efe5b312ba8fcd9c","tid":1939101,"uid":192745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T03:07:42.000Z","msg":"今日本應係6周年記念日，但係係一個月多前妳同我講話冇左愛既感覺，我真係好傷好痛，我知道愛情係自私既，但係6年的回憶，我們的第一日拍拖情景，我當時係戲院拖妳手，個喜歡的感覺喜悅既笑容，我都永遠會記住，6年來我們一同經歷好多人生既事，一齊傾講解決，一齊開心一齊傷心，我們都成為彼此的一部份，妳教識我學懂愛與珍惜，上進努力，感謝妳過去6年帶給我的所有，這6年是我人生中過得好幸福好有愛的時光，yu 謝謝妳"},{"pid":"bc40d6b8b5ffd99e6fb3e68b70ab50265d25d6a8","tid":1939101,"uid":162539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T05:34:36.000Z","msg":"係咪遇到第二個？"},{"pid":"ca778500aaa722b0b9c801ee9eb2fec6dceb02f8","tid":1939101,"uid":192745,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc40d6b8b5ffd99e6fb3e68b70ab50265d25d6a8","tid":1939101,"uid":162539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T05:34:36.000Z","msg":"係咪遇到第二個？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T10:25:38.000Z","msg":"佢話係分左手後先同新果個一齊&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"9cc072d3d458e5215d1f428ce1d982f32ceb77f1","tid":1939101,"uid":105980,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ca778500aaa722b0b9c801ee9eb2fec6dceb02f8","tid":1939101,"uid":192745,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc40d6b8b5ffd99e6fb3e68b70ab50265d25d6a8","tid":1939101,"uid":162539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T05:34:36.000Z","msg":"係咪遇到第二個？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T10:25:38.000Z","msg":"佢話係分左手後先同新果個一齊&hellip;&hellip;"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T10:41:00.000Z","msg":"你相信？"},{"pid":"2e4f951b290105b07c82a4d8c4fcb0c94ce825bc","tid":1939101,"uid":192745,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9cc072d3d458e5215d1f428ce1d982f32ceb77f1","tid":1939101,"uid":105980,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ca778500aaa722b0b9c801ee9eb2fec6dceb02f8","tid":1939101,"uid":1927